"This documentary offers an insight into the private world of Clarence House by examining the rise and fall of its key servant, WILLIAM TALLON, butler to the Queen Mother - or Page of the Backstairs, to give him his proper title. From this exalted and powerful position, Backstairs Billy, as he came to be known, saw and heard everything; but, despite huge cash offers, he never spilled the beans."
